         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">17/1/82. ¶  ¶ That ¶  was a sad intelligence, dear Sir Joseph, that of poor Dr Sonder's death! ¶  So he is gone  ¶ before me ¶ , the friend of my youth, the genial and disinterested promotor of my res...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">82.01.17b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Joseph Hooker</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RBG Kew, Kew Correspondence, Australia, Mueller, 1882-90, f. 1.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">17/1/82.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">That</hi>
               </seg> was a sad intelligence, dear Sir Joseph, that of poor Dr Sonder's death!<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sonder died on 21 November 1881.</p>
               </note> So he is gone <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">before me</hi>
               </seg>, the friend of my youth, the genial and disinterested promotor of my researches through 33 years, over which my regular correspondence from Australia with him has extended. O! How shall I miss <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">such</hi>
               </seg> a friend, so dear, so disinterested, so willing to aid and encourage! One of the strongest threads, which tied me to scientific life, is torn asunder!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>He died after only 4 days illness from a severe form of influenza; his last letter, on the first day of his ailing, was written to me.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found.</p>
               </note> I telegraphed to the mournful widow my condolence,<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Telegram not found.</p>
               </note> who writes a distressing letter,<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found.</p>
               </note> that in the fever-dreams of his last days he was much speaking about the few Algs he had recently from me. How shall I miss <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">his</hi>
               </seg> kind letters, which always encouraged me in my troubles and alleviated so much the sadness of my later years.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
